*clamav-0.97 (22 Feb 2011)

  22 Feb 2011; Tim Harder <radhermit@gentoo.org> +clamav-0.97.ebuild,
  +files/clamav-0.97-nls.patch:
  Version bump (bug #354019) with ebuild updates thanks to Bernd Lommerzheim.
  Update to EAPI 4, don't install signature files (fixes bugs #336842 and
  #345965), remove dependencies in the system set, update zlib dependency,
  other minor cleanups and style changes.

  07 Jan 2011; Kacper Kowalik <xarthisius@gentoo.org> clamav-0.96.5.ebuild:
  stable ppc64 wrt #347627

  07 Jan 2011; Brent Baude <ranger@gentoo.org> clamav-0.96.4.ebuild:
  Marking clamav-0.96.4 ppc64 for bug 338226

  12 Dec 2010; Raúl Porcel <armin76@gentoo.org> clamav-0.96.5.ebuild:
  alpha/ia64/sparc stable wrt #347627

  07 Dec 2010; Brent Baude <ranger@gentoo.org> clamav-0.96.5.ebuild:
  Marking clamav-0.96.5 ppc for bug 347627

